22/03/2010
TIRANA, Albania -- Police seized one tonne of marijuana Saturday (March 20th) in the village of Kakome, near Saranda, and made one arrest.
The stash was about to be loaded into a vehicle bound for Italy, authorities said on Sunday.
Several days ago, police seized another stash of 636kg of marijuana in the nearby village of Bunec.
(Shekulli, News 24, Top News, Lajmifundit - 21/03/10)
